Read a directory's contents, recursively; see
\*(T<\fB\-\-path\fR\*(T>.
.RE
.TP 
\*(T<\fB\-\-path\fR\*(T>
Directory in which to look for music. Use with
\*(T<\fB\-\-backend\fR\*(T>=dir.
.TP 
\*(T<\fB\-b\fR\*(T>, \*(T<\fB\-\-bitrate\fR\*(T>
